&ldquo;Wizard skill: Understand your abstractions (sometimes)&rdquo; - Julia Evans Statically compiled languages, like Go, are quiet popular these days. In combination with another blockbuster technology, Docker containers, a big advantage is the minimal size of the resulting container image. This can be achieved by using the special (and reserved) Docker scratch image.
